&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Bash Variables</title><link>https://pwsh.in/notes/bash/basic/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://pwsh.in/notes/bash/basic/</guid><description>&lt;!-- Variable -->
